short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Modify YouTube thumbnails to include DougDoug

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Enhance your browsing experience with DougDougify. Is your youtube homepage boring and lacking bald men? Are you bored because you are stuck in Dougs basement? Are you sad because your wife just divorced you and DougDoug didn't upload today? PANIC! This extension is rigged to add DougDoug to every thumbnail.

Compatible with all browsers
If you are experiencing issues, report them on Github
For discussion about this extension, go to my Discord: http://discord.gg/bQvtauxXWp

Notes: 
- This extension was inspired by Unnecessary Inventions: http://www.youtube.com/@UnnecessaryInventions
- This extension is unofficial and not affiliated with DougDoug or YouTube.
Source: http://github.com/MagicJinn/Youtube-DougDougify
